{"id":"7767","user":{"id":"101860","nickname":"四片叶de三叶吖","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FqcR23gyTBxqpGDVypZpJe8hw4uq","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第一课：BOX2.0—尚冲教你如何把一个火柴盒变的高大上！","content":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhtskRMaTn49pa6uFCmArOZbZA-E\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 尚冲：“本人受到上次“杯具”已经不想说什么啦····”<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/9d/sada_thumb.gif\"></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ffcc00\" size=\"5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;=============完美分割线===============</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"5\">尚冲：“大家好，我是11号少院士—尚冲，我要做建筑教学啦！”</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 尚冲：“玩过mc的人都知道，可以自由建筑是mc一大特色。”</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 尚冲：“现在，不管是mc的dalao，还是萌新，大家肯定都建过这样的火柴盒”</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhUZWdNrPcl5Vba7Tbu7enlbaXY4\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color=\"#c0c0c0\">&nbsp;（代码岛的还原图）</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<font size=\"5\"> 尚冲：“我们今天就是在这个基础上，做出一个大别墅！建筑的材料是石木”</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 尚冲：“先加入木头支柱，使它增加一些棱角感 。”</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhW2QgAvCG1bJfQxDrNPZWeHUhU4\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<font size=\"5\"> 尚冲：“在进行进一步修饰”</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fo3UFWPTSMm6_Go47azFPt9dUFO_\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font color=\"#808080\">（凭个人喜好修饰）</font></font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#808080\" size=\"5\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font size=\"5\">尚冲：“可以再加一个二层”</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FsAOe84ZqKTAJyFRifkKr3lEeA-c\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"5\">尚冲：“加门廊，是为了做出一楼和二楼的区别，也为二楼提供了一个小阳台。”</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 尚冲：“可以先封个顶。”</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fu1FAMW54FuWOitR3tcL3-ics7Sx\"><br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FlnQM9faWZSl6DDjNgExGQUK-6lT\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"5\">&nbsp;尚冲：“这样的平顶是很丑的，所以坡形屋顶是必不可缺的，还可以再加一个小阁楼。”</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fr7qc5Ntaq8GguQX1stl7HUAPKkI\"><br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpqafwZjEHe7qFJgwemSGYUNBXxh\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"5\">尚冲：“什么？全木屋顶不够漂亮？一招教你改变它”&nbsp;<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 在屋顶一周增加石砖边框，和石砖横梁。</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhWPMtbcBMMTUQXbZKy4Z0QEu8eH\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"5\">尚冲：“以上是示例。”</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; 尚冲：“就这么完啦？不，才刚刚开始，细节来啦！”</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;注意屋顶</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fjw7m3vwn7js5GhBBmZc-fHJt3EL\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"5\">（ 做出向内凹陷的屋顶）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;对比一下之前的墙壁</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgI1-xOs86iJy2unUCUDb-5MNW7k\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"5\">（增加一些墙壁的凹凸感）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 远观</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fsz5TmLGg4x9t8NoW-37AKlowfuZ\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"5\">可以再增加一些藤蔓</font><font size=\"2\">（ps：其实是树叶）</font><font size=\"5\"></font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FiUQg3hwP7ewiaBIPXmZwsxNldYr\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"7\">&nbsp; 全景</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrHZzutDu4RFlZkIwKbQbm9KWNve\"><br></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ffcc00\">===================================================================</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgMSpCHIAWbTUSUd0RxZFvLFmMqA\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<font size=\"5\"> 尚冲：“一个人，坐在自己亲手打造的家中的阳台，遥望远方的星空，是不是很有feel~”</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>（PS：此贴为建筑教学帖，所以以图为主，为新人建筑师所写，欢迎dalao指点）</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\">&nbsp;<font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">THANKS FOR YOUR READING!</font><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &n